    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey quick question, im taking sertraline for my mood but finals week is coming up and i feel super low and drained. i was thinking about adding some st johns wort to my routine to help boost my energy/mood naturally since the sertraline isn't quite hitting the spot lately. is it cool to take them together??",
